416	19 	Study	Female	To see how easily influenced we are by the facts we are given on people and how this impacts our impression of the person and whether we associate them with positive or negative things	I think the part where we had to indicate whether something was positive or negative and whether it was Bob or not was interesting, particularly when the key that corresponded to Bob switched. I found it easier when Bob was framed negatively because in the switch, he would then be paired with negative words. When he was framed positively yet paired with the same key for negative words, I hesitated much more